{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "唐方、唐朋在大渡河铁索桥上遭遇被梁消暑、戚常戚押送的马竟终和欧阳珊一，以及神秘的‘药王’莫非冤。唐方唐朋立即动手救援，左丘超然趁机从桥另一端暗杀四名帮徒和戚常戚，解救了马竟终夫妇。但药王以‘无形之毒’在对话间下毒，众人纷纷中毒倒地。唐朋临倒前发出‘子母离魂镖’绝杀，迫使药王跳江避镖，母镖击杀梁消暑。众人被药王擒获改装押走，马竟终坠江后自救清醒，暗中跟踪药王一行入川至清水河一带。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_peng",
      "speaker_name": "唐朋",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_tang_peng",
      "text": "你听过满脸病容的‘毒手药王’，有没有听说过满脸笑容的‘药王’？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_peng",
      "speaker_name": "唐朋",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "‘药王’莫非冤？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_tang_peng",
      "text": "你既知我大名，便死得不冤。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_tang_peng",
      "text": "哪，你的东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_tang_peng",
      "text": "药王的东西碰不得的！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小女孩好聪明。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "我最喜欢聪明的女子，我最喜欢给这种女孩子吃我的药……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们之所以在大渡河桥上相遇，如此凑巧，却是为何，你们可知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "我跟踪你们已久，一直图营救马兄嫂，而今才等到机会。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "哪有这麽容易！我们之所以带这两人到处走，就是为了要引你这漏纲之鱼出来领死！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "不过现在还不是给我们救了过来，还杀了你们五人！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "不错，那是我们没意料到会在这儿遇上唐家姊弟，不过……你们也敌不过我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "那要打过才知。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "理当如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "你动手吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "我已经动手啦。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_shan_yi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳珊一",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "什麽时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_shan_yi",
      "text": "刚才，就在我跟你们说完的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "狗贼，我们来一分胜负。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "不必分了，你们已败。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "你……下了……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "我早已在对话问下了‘无形之毒’，你们已中毒了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "text": "你……怎样……下的毒？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_fei_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "莫非冤",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "text": "就在我说话的时候，毒就放了……就在你们说话的时候，毒就到了你们的舌头。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们‘药王’名动天下，要毒你们几个小子，还不容易？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倒也，倒也，饶是你恶似鬼，也得喝老于洗脚水……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_peng",
      "speaker_name": "唐朋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "……我们毕竟杀了你们这对奸夫恶妇。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 17
    }
  ],
